# TRADING ALERTS APP - CURSOR RULES (ENGLISH)

## GLOBAL RULES
- ALL code, comments, variable names, UI text in ENGLISH
- Use Heroicons or Lucide icons ONLY (no emoji, no WhatsApp icons)
- Minimal icons: only where essential for UX (settings, chat, refresh)
- Clean, professional Revolut-style design (no decorative icons)

## CODING STYLE
- ES6+ (const/let, arrow functions, async/await)
- Max 100 chars/line
- Comments ONLY for complex logic (no obvious comments)
- Error handling: try/catch on ALL async functions
- Validate inputs before processing
- API responses: { success: boolean, data: any, error: string }

## AGENT MODE BEHAVIOR
- Test each module immediately after creation
- Backend: npm install && npm start && test endpoints
- Frontend: open index.html && check console
- Fix errors before proceeding to next module
- Never leave TODO/FIXME/placeholders

## ITERATION LOOP
1. Implement module
2. Test functionality
3. If error -> analyze cause -> fix -> re-test
4. Only proceed when tests pass
5. Document fixes in commit message

