Mobile-first: start with 375px, add media queries for 768px+

## AI CHAT SPECIAL
- Multi-mode detection: analyze question and respond from relevant perspectives
- ALWAYS concise (max 250 words)
- Respond in SAME language as user query
- Structure: Analysis -> Key insights -> Actionable info

## SYMBOLS SOURCE
- Fetch from Yahoo Finance API (S&P 500 or top volume)
- Auto-update weekly
- Fallback to cached top100.json

## TESTING CHECKLIST (execute after each module)
Backend:
- npm install succeeds
- npm start no errors
- curl endpoints return 200 OK
- Error handling works (invalid inputs)

Frontend:
- index.html opens no console errors
- Responsive at 375px, 768px, 1024px
- All buttons/interactions work
- LocalStorage persists

Integration:
- Frontend API calls succeed
- AI responds (<5s)
- Notifications request permission correctly
